name: Antis Inu
description: Antis Inu will be the very first meme token to defeat the falling Shiba army! During World War II, the famous dog Antis was the first canine to fly as part of military air raids. He will now be raiding the Binance blockchain and taking back what is rightfully his. The Shiba Inu species almost went extinct towards the end of World War II from air raids led by Antis. Antis will not fail his mission this time around.
